# Lab 2: MFA & Conditional Access

## Objective
Implement Zero Trust access controls using MFA and Conditional Access policies in Azure.

## Tasks Performed
- Created break-glass admin account
- Enabled MFA for standard users
- Designed Conditional Access policy enforcing MFA
- Tested sign-in behavior and access logs

## Security Concepts Applied
- Zero Trust
- Defense in depth
- Identity protection
- Risk reduction

## Outcome
User access is protected with MFA while maintaining administrative recovery paths.
